<bibRefCitation author="Heie O. E." box="[475,624,1559,1585]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" refId="ref10988" refString="Heie O. E. 1994. The Aphidoidea of Fennoscandia and Denmark V. Aphidinae. Part 2 of Macrosiphini. Fauna Entomologica Scandinavica 28. E. J. Brill, Leiden-New York-Koln." type="book" year="1994">Heie (1994)</bibRefCitation>
. Abdominal dorsum membranous, segmental borders distinct. Apt. about 
<quantity box="[299,370,1594,1621]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.0" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" unit="mm" value="4.0">4 mm</quantity>
, green, yellowish or reddish. Ant. segment 3 with more than 30 rhinaria. Monoecious.
</paragraph>
